ABSTRACT
In one embodiment, a method for generating a recom-
mended change to a communication behavior of a first user
of a network includes identifying a communication pattern
in accordance with data extracted from communications
collected in the network, wherein the data is associated with
at least one of the first user and an endpoint other than the
first user, and generating the recommended change based on
the communication pattern, where the recommended change
is to the communication behavior of the first user.
